nodes.text: Jana Vance is a foley artist at Skywalker Sound. She worked on Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace, Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones, Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith, Star Wars: Republic Commando, the Star Wars: The Clone Wars film and it's 2008 series, Star Wars: The Force Unleashed, Star Wars: The Force Unleashed: Ultimate Sith Edition, Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II, LEGO Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Out, Star Wars: Battlefront, Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens, Vader Immortal: A Star Wars VR Series – Episode I, The Mandalorian, and Star Wars Resistance.
